languages.text: Kibellah quiere atender otro evento social. Sin embargo, esta vez debe celebrarse en Dargonus. Janris Danrok estará esperando a{mf|l| la} Lord Capitán en el palacio para dar comienzo a la velada.
languages.original_text: Kibellah wishes to attend another social function. However, this one is to take place on Dargonus. Janris Danrok will be waiting for the Lord Captain at the palace to commence the event.

languages.text: キベラはまた、別の社交行事に参加したいという。しかし、今回はダルゴナスで開催されるものだ。ジャンリス・ダンロックが宮殿でロード・キャプテンを迎え、催しを開催するべく待機している。
languages.original_text: Kibellah wishes to attend another social function. However, this one is to take place on Dargonus. Janris Danrok will be waiting for the Lord Captain at the palace to commence the event.

languages.text: 绮贝菈希望能参加另一场社交活动。不过，这场社交活动将会在达戈努斯举办，詹里斯·丹罗克会在宫殿里等待行商浪人宣布召开典礼。
languages.original_text: Kibellah wishes to attend another social function. However, this one is to take place on Dargonus. Janris Danrok will be waiting for the Lord Captain at the palace to commence the event.

languages.text: Kibellah möchte eine andere soziale Funktion ausüben. Allerdings ist diese an Dargonus gebunden. Janris Danrok erwartet den Lord Captain am Palast, um mit der Veranstaltung fortzufahren.
languages.original_text: Kibellah wishes to attend another social function. However, this one is to take place on Dargonus. Janris Danrok will be waiting for the Lord Captain at the palace to commence the event.

languages.text: Kibellah souhaite participer à un autre événement mondain. Toutefois, le prochain aura lieu sur Dargonus. Janris Danrok attend le feu vert {mf|du seigneur-capitaine|de la seigneure-capitaine} au palais pour commencer l'événement.
languages.original_text: Kibellah wishes to attend another social function. However, this one is to take place on Dargonus. Janris Danrok will be waiting for the Lord Captain at the palace to commence the event.

languages.text: Kibellah, başka bir sosyal etkinliğe daha katılmak istiyor. Ancak bu seferki etkinlik Dargonus'ta gerçekleşiyor. Janris Danrok, etkinliği başlatmak için sarayda Lord Kaptan'ı bekleyecek.
